      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA procedures documented under FDA 21 CFR Part 820 design controls; version-controlled simulation environment with audit trail; requiredLevel 2 reflects medium model influence with confirmatory testing.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under validated installation qualification (IQ/OQ). DePuy Synthes and FDA simulation environments independently version-controlled. Change management logs reviewed. Achieved level 3 reflects additional cross-platform consistency checks between three independent modeling teams."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
