    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Eleven of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. Two factors (Use error, Equivalency of input parameters) carry their acceptance rationale embedded in the rationale field rather than as a separate structured acceptanceCriteria entry, which represents a documentation gap to be remediated in the next revision. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the COU is explicitly bounded to the ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration and no extrapolation to other loading conditions is claimed. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a medium-assurance regulatory submission for this Class II device.",
